{"tid":443384,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"據 IMDb 報導《Iron Man 3》關鍵角色將加入《Avengers 4》","createTime":"2017-10-21T14:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T15:26:47.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3fe240e05c4ae483ef27e3a12693006b2bb78d","tid":443384,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"記得《Iron Man 3》中由美國童星 Ty Simpkins 飾演，在戲中替墜毀的 Tony Stark 打氣並走出迷思的小幫手 Harley Keener 嗎？根據 IMDb 報導，Ty Simpkins 將回鍋演出 2019 年上映， MCU 的第三階段終幕之作《Avengers 4》。<br />\n<br />\n由於&nbsp;Robert Downey Jr.多次表示自己將在《Avengers 4》結束後，考慮正式從 Iron Man 這個經典角色退役，也讓現年 16 歲的 Ty Simpkins 被外界視為接棒 Iron Man 的熱門人選之一。此番 Marvel Studios 找來 Ty Simpkins 演出《Avengers 4》，用意是否在於將 Iron Man 的角色於此即電影內，正式由 Robert Downey Jr.手中傳承給 Ty Simpkins，目前不得而知。<br />\n<br />\n不過可以確定的是 Ty Simpkins 的回歸，將讓錯綜複雜的《Avengers 4》故事情節更為豐富生動。通算為 MCU 第 22 部作品的《Avengers 4》，暫定將於 2019 年 5 月 3 日在全美上映。"},{"pid":"2735cd189dcd83c521f791e4b470fd59f844bcdc","tid":443384,"uid":48791,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"logan"},{"pid":"3557f065766b536a4eb1de74d1339e47a6a45d4f","tid":443384,"uid":48741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係同一架但都係豪華房車"},{"pid":"aa55b26a0d8d98b4134259858c20152591092d9c","tid":443384,"uid":40306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:23:28.000Z","msg":"如果係伏線既話就真心屈機"},{"pid":"b14181bc2655d3d8d337bbfced92a3771a7db88f","tid":443384,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"cf0c0e87373b99250d95876093742286bdc40244","tid":443384,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:28:13.000Z","msg":"唔通真係幫tony送殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7cea67d8f0db11cc56b0bbbdf2d2d6c5f01450","tid":443384,"uid":41343